screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Please enter the individual's height in inches.
Enter the individual's weight in kilograms.
Has a doctor ever told you that you have inflammatory arthritis?
Do you often experience sudden joint pain, or early morning joint stiffness lasting longer than 30 minutes after rising from bed?
Are you receiving treatment for inflammatory arthritis?
Has a doctor ever told you that you have anemia?
Have you ever been diagnosed with cancer?
Have you ever been diagnosed with oral cancer?
Do you have any recurring or non-healing ulcers in the mouth? These ulcers may be painful or painless.
Are you having any problems with your gums or teeth? This may include dental caries, tooth or gum pain, lost tooth, or need for new or replaced dentures.
Do you have cataracts?
Have you visited the eye doctor in the past 12 months?
Do you have diabetes?
Have you ever been diagnosed with gestational diabetes?
Are you taking insulin to control your diabetes?
Has a doctor ever told you that you have hypertension or high blood pressure?
Are you taking prescribed medication to lower your blood pressure or cholesterol?
Have you experienced severe headaches, nose bleeds, or vision problems in the past week?
Have you ever been diagnosed with any psychiatric problems? This may include schizophrenia, depression, or other mood disorders.
Are you taking any psychiatric medications?
Do you often experience feelings of sadness or depression?
Do you think anyone in your family needs psychiatric consultation or help with mental health issues?
Have you experienced fever with chills or shaking in the past 1 week?
Are you receiving cancer treatment or doing regular follow up with a doctor for cancer?
Do any of the following apply to you? (select all that apply).
Have you noticed blood in the urine in the past 3 months?
Have you noticed a significant increase or decrease in urine output in the past 3 months?
Have you ever been on dialysis for kidney disease?
Have you ever been diagnosed with a stone in the kidney or bladder?
Have you ever had a cough lasting longer than 3 weeks with fever and weight loss?
Have you ever had close contact with someone who is sick with tuberculosis?
Have you been vaccinated for tuberculosis?
Have you had an Eschar (the painless black crust at the site of a mite bite)?
Have you ever consumed alcohol (beer, wine, spirits, etc.)?
Has your drinking ever negatively affected your daily life, or has anyone close to you expressed concern about your alcohol consumption?
Have you ever used tobacco products? This may include cigarettes, chewing tobacco, vapes, cigars, etc.
How often have you used tobacco in the past 3 months?
Have you ever tried and failed to control, cut down on, or stop using tobacco? If not, would you like to quit?
Have you ever used drugs in the past 6 months? Drugs may include: marijuana, cocaine, amphetamines, inhalants, sedatives, hallucinogens, or opioids.
Are you taking vitamin supplements?
Are you a vegan or strict vegetarian?
Were you bitten by a dog in the past 3 days?
Have you ever been bitten by a snake?
Would you like to know your blood group?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Sngewbha ban pynrung ia ka jingjrong jong ki briew ha ka inshi
Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong I briew ha ka kilo
Hato la ju lap ba ki duna snam?
Hato ki shah sumar na ka jingpang duna snam ne anemia?
Hato ki don sahiaw?
Ha kine ki taiew ba la dep, hato phi sngew donkam ban tang haduh 10 tam na u jingtan ba iarap ring mynsiem ne inhaler (ne u short-acting bronchodilator kum u  Ventolin) ha kano kano ka sngi.
Hato phi tharai ba I la ioh ia ka jingpang flu? Ki dak ki shin ka jingpang flu; mih eitmut lane set khmut, set ryndang, shimet suh khriat, jyrhoh, bad thait.
Hato ki la shim lia ka tika iaid na ka jingpang flu ha kane ka aiom ba ioh pang flu?
I lah ioh shimet bad ka khynniuh khriat ha kine ki taiew ba la dep
Hato ki ioh jingshit bad ki khniang/ ne saw ki khmat?
Hato I lah ioh jyrhoh kaba la neh palat ia ka 3 taiew bad ka jingshit bad hiar ka jingkhia?
Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan ba I briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato I khun jong phii la shim ia ka tika ban iada ia ka jingpang tubercuosis ha ka por ba dang kha?
Hato ki la ju khoh ne em ka sniehdoh (Kane ka sniehdoh ba khoh ka long rong iong kaba khoh na ka jaka ba shah diat khniang hynrei kam long kaba pang)?
Hato ki bam ne dih ia ki jingbam ia ki dawai vitamin?
Hato phim ju bam doh ne phi dei iba bam beit tang da ki jingbam ba shna na ki jhur bad ki jingthung ne vegan?
Hato ki la ju shah dait ksew ha kine ki 3 sngi ba la dep?
Hato phi la ju shah puh bsein?
Phi kwah ban tip ia ka blood group jong I khun?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Please enter the individual's height in inches.
Enter the individual's weight in kilograms.
Has a doctor ever told you that you have anemia?

Have you noticed a significant increase or decrease in urine output in the past 3 months?
Have you ever been on dialysis for kidney disease?
Have you ever been diagnosed with a stone in the kidney or bladder?
Have you experienced fever with chills or shaking in the past 1 week?
Have you ever had a cough lasting longer than 3 weeks with fever and weight loss?
Have you ever had close contact with someone who is sick with tuberculosis?
Have you been vaccinated for tuberculosis?
Have you ever consumed alcohol (beer, wine, spirits, etc.)?
Have you ever used tobacco products? This may include cigarettes, chewing tobacco, vapes, cigars, etc.
Have you ever used drugs in the past 6 months? Drugs may include: marijuana, cocaine, amphetamines, inhalants, sedatives, hallucinogens, or opioids.
Are you taking vitamin supplements?
Are you a strict vegetarian?
Were you bitten by a dog in the past 3 days?
Have you ever been bitten by a snake?
Would you like to know your blood group?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Sngewbha ban thoh ia ka jingjrong jong ki briew da ka inshi
Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong i briew da ka kilo
La ju don mo i doktor iba ong ia phi ba phi duna snam?
Hato phi don jingpang sahiaw?
Hato phi ju ioh mad barabor ba phi jyrhoh bad jynjar ban ring mynsiem kaba ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi?
Hato phi don jingpang shini?
Hato i doktor i la ong ia phi ba phi kiew ka blood pressure?
Hato phi la ju ioh mad ia ka jingktha khlieh kaba palat, mih 'nam sohmut, ne bym iohi ha kine ki taiew ba la leit?
Hato ki la ju lap ba phi don jingpang bampong ha shyntur?
Hato phi ju don ki jingmong kiba mih man la ka por ha shyntur ne ki bym jem shuh? Kine ki jingmong ki lah ban long kiba pang bad ki bym pang.
Hato phi don kino kino ki jingthut ha ki dohbniat ne ki bniat? Kane ka lah ban kynthup ia ka jingbam khniang ki bniat, pang ki bniat bad doh bniat, kdiah bniat, ne donkam ban thung da kiwei ki bniat
Hato phi la ju leit pynjhieh da ka snam ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju kynmaw ban peit ia ka jingbun ne jingduna ka umpynjhieh ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju hap ban leh dialysis namar ka jingpang khyllai?
Hato ki la lap ia phi ba don maw ha khyllai lane ha ka pla um pynjhieh?
Hato phi la ju ioh ia ka jingpang shitmet bad suh khriat ha kane ka shitaiew ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju jyrhoh kaba neh haduh 3 taiew ryngkat bad ka jingshit bad ka jinghiar ka jingkhia?
Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan i briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato phi la shim tika iada na ka jingpang tuberculosis?
Hato phi la ju dih kyiad (beer, wine, spirit bad kiwei kiwei)?
Hato ka jingdih kyiad jong phi ka la ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi, lane hato ki briew ba iajan bad phi ki la pynpaw ia ka jingsngewkhia ha kaba iadei bad ka jingdih kyiad jong phi?
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam kino kino ki jingbam kiba la shna na u duma? Kine ki kynthup ia u sikret, duma, vapes, u shrut bad kiwei kiwei?

Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia u drok ha kine ki 6 bnai ba la leit? Ki drok ki kynthup ia: u kynja,  amphetamines, ki drok ba shu tan ne inhalants, ki drok ba pynbuaid ne sedatives, ki drok ba pyni ia kaei kaei ka bym don ne hallucinogens, lane u opioids
Hato phi dih dawai vitamin?
Are you a strict vegetarian?
Hato phi la ju shah dait ksew ha kine ki 3 sngi ba la leit?
Phi don ksew ha iing lane ksew surok hajan iing?
Hato phi la ju shah puh bsein?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Sngewbha ban thoh ia ka jingjrong jong ki briew da ka inshi
Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong i briew da ka kilo
La ju don mo i doktor iba ong ia phi ba phi duna snam?
Hato phi leit shah sumar na ka jingpang anemia?
Hato phi don jingpang sahiaw?
Hato phi ju ioh mad barabor ba phi jyrhoh bad jynjar ban ring mynsiem kaba ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi?
Hato phi don jingpang shini?
Hato i doktor i la ong ia phi ba phi kiew ka blood pressure?
Hato phi la ju ioh mad ia ka jingktha khlieh kaba palat, mih 'nam sohmut, ne bym iohi ha kine ki taiew ba la leit?
Hato lah ju lap ia phi da ki doktor ba phi don jingshitom ha ka bor pyrkhat? Kane ka kynthup ia ka jingpang schizophrenia (iohi rngai), ka jingsngewdiaw ne kiwei kiwei ki jingthut?
Hato phi dih kino kino ki dawai kiba iadei bad ka bor pyrkhat?
Hato phi ju mad barabor ia ka jinglong sngewsih?
Hato phi tharai don mano mano na iing jong phi kiba donkam ban iakynduh ia ki doktor ba khmih ia ka bor pyrkhat ne ban iarap ia ki na ka jingpang jong ka jingduna bor pyrkhat?
Hato phi la ju jyrhoh kaba neh haduh 3 taiew ryngkat bad ka jingshit bad ka jinghiar ka jingkhia?
Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan i briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato phi la shim tika iada na ka jingpang tuberculosis?
Hato phi la ju ioh ia ka jingpang shitmet bad suh khriat ha kane ka shitaiew ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju dih kyiad (beer, wine, spirit bad kiwei kiwei)?
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia kino kino ki kynja duma? Kine ki lah ban long u sikret, u duma, u shrut bad kiwei kiwei
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia kino kino ki kynja drok ha kine ki 6 bnai ba la leit?
Hato phi dih dawai vitamin?
Hato phi long iba pyrkhing bha ha ka rukom bam kata ban bam beit thik tang da ki jhur?
Hato phi la ju shah dait ksew ha kine ki 3 sngi ba la leit?
Phi don ksew ha iing lane ksew surok hajan iing?
Hato phi la ju shah puh bsein?
Hato phi ju iohi barobor ia ki bsein?
Phi kwah ban tip ia ka blood group jong phi?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Sngewbha ban thoh ia ka jingjrong jong ki briew da ka inshi
Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong i briew da ka kilo
La ju don mo i doktor iba ong ia phi ba phi duna snam?
Hato phi don jingpang sahiaw?
Hato phi ju ioh mad barabor ba phi jyrhoh bad jynjar ban ring mynsiem kaba ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi?
Hato phi don jingpang shini?
Hato phi pyndonkam ia ka insulin ba pynduna ia ka jingpang shini?
Hato i doktor i la ong ia phi ba phi kiew ka blood pressure?
Hato phi la ju ioh mad ia ka jingktha khlieh kaba palat, mih 'nam sohmut, ne bym iohi ha kine ki taiew ba la leit?
Hato ki la ju lap ba phi don jingpang bampong ha shyntur?
Hato phi ju don ki jingmong kiba mih man la ka por ha shyntur ne ki bym jem shuh? Kine ki jingmong ki lah ban long kiba pang bad ki bym pang.
Hato phi don kino kino ki jingthut ha ki dohbniat ne ki bniat? Kane ka lah ban kynthup ia ka jingbam khniang ki bniat, pang ki bniat bad doh bniat, kdiah bniat, ne donkam ban thung da kiwei ki bniat
Hato phi la ju leit pynjhieh da ka snam ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju kynmaw ban peit ia ka jingbun ne jingduna ka umpynjhieh ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju hap ban leh dialysis namar ka jingpang khyllai?
Hato ki la lap ia phi ba don maw ha khyllai lane ha ka pla um pynjhieh?
Hato phi la ju ioh ia ka jingpang shitmet bad suh khriat ha kane ka shitaiew ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju jyrhoh kaba neh haduh 3 taiew ryngkat bad ka jingshit bad ka jinghiar ka jingkhia?
Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan i briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato phi la shim tika iada na ka jingpang tuberculosis?
Hato phi la ju dih kyiad (beer, wine, spirit bad kiwei kiwei)?
Hato ka jingdih kyiad jong phi ka la ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi, lane hato ki briew ba iajan bad phi ki la pynpaw ia ka jingsngewkhia ha kaba iadei bad ka jingdih kyiad jong phi?
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia kino kino ki kynja duma? Kine ki lah ban long u sikret, u duma, u shrut bad kiwei kiwei
Katno sien phi dih ne bam duma ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?

screeningQuestionAnswer.question: Sngewbha ban thoh ia ka jingjrong jong ki briew da ka inshi
Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong i briew da ka kilo
La ju don mo i doktor iba ong ia phi ba phi duna snam?
Hato phi don jingpang sahiaw?
Ha kine ki taiew ba la leit, hato phi sngew donkam ban tan haduh 10 tan na u jingtan ba iarap ring mynsiem ne inhaler (ne u short-acting bronchodilator kum u  Ventolin) ha kano kano ka sngi.
Hato phi la leit iakynduh doktor ha kine ki 6 bnai ba la leit ha kaba iadei bad ka jingpang sahiaw?
Hato phi don jingpang shini?
Hato la ju lap ia phi ba phi don ka jingpang shini ha ka por ba phi armet?
Hato phi pyndonkam ia ka insulin ba pynduna ia ka jingpang shini?
Hato i doktor i la ong ia phi ba phi kiew ka blood pressure?
Hato phi la dih dawai ban pynduna ia ka blood pressure ne cholesterol?
Hato phi la ju ioh mad ia ka jingktha khlieh kaba palat, mih 'nam sohmut, ne bym iohi ha kine ki taiew ba la leit?
Hato lah ju lap ia phi da ki doktor ba phi don jingshitom ha ka bor pyrkhat? Kane ka kynthup ia ka jingpang schizophrenia (iohi rngai), ka jingsngewdiaw ne kiwei kiwei ki jingthut?
Hato phi dih kino kino ki dawai kiba iadei bad ka bor pyrkhat?
Hato phi ju mad barabor ia ka jinglong sngewsih?
Hato phi tharai don mano mano na iing jong phi kiba donkam ban iakynduh ia ki doktor ba khmih ia ka bor pyrkhat ne ban iarap ia ki na ka jingpang jong ka jingduna bor pyrkhat?
Hato phi la ju jyrhoh kaba neh haduh 3 taiew ryngkat bad ka jingshit bad ka jinghiar ka jingkhia?
Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan i briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato phi la shim tika iada na ka jingpang tuberculosis?
Hato phi la ju ioh ia ka jingpang shitmet bad suh khriat ha kane ka shitaiew ba la leit?
Hato phi la ju dih kyiad (beer, wine, spirit bad kiwei kiwei)?
Hato ka jingdih kyiad jong phi ka la ktah ia ka jingim jong phi ba man la ka sngi, lane hato ki briew ba iajan bad phi ki la pynpaw ia ka jingsngewkhia ha kaba iadei bad ka jingdih kyiad jong phi?
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia kino kino ki kynja duma? Kine ki lah ban long u sikret, u duma, u shrut bad kiwei kiwei
Katno sien phi dih ne bam duma ha kine ki 3 bnai ba la leit?
screeningQuestionAnswer.answer: Man ka sngi ne jan man ka sngi

Thoh ia ka jingkhia jong i briew da ka kilo
La ju don mo i doktor iba ong ia phi ba phi duna snam?

Hato phi la iakynduh ne don hajan i briew iba pang Tuberculosis?
Hato phi la shim tika iada na ka jingpang tuberculosis?
Hato phi la ju dih kyiad (beer, wine, spirit bad kiwei kiwei)?
Hato phi la ju pyndonkam ia kino kino ki kynja duma? Kine ki lah ban long u sikret, u duma, u shrut bad kiwei kiwei

Hato phi dih dawai vitamin?
